  "prompt": "Is there any availability in Prestige Falcon City?",
  "response": "As of my last update, Prestige Falcon City is a popular residential complex in Bangalore, and availability can fluctuate frequently due to its demand. For the most current information on availability, I recommend the following options:\n\n1. **Contact Prestige Falcon City Directly**: You can reach out to the sales or management office of Prestige Falcon City. Their contact details are usually available on their official website or through a quick online search.\n\n2. **Real Estate Websites**: Platforms like Magicbricks, 99acres, or Housing.com often list properties available for sale or rent in Prestige Falcon City. These sites are updated regularly, but it's always good to double-check with the property management.\n\n3. **Real Estate Agents**: Local agents who specialize in properties in Bangalore, particularly in the area where Prestige Falcon City is located, can provide detailed and current information on availability.\n\n4. **Visit in Person**: If feasible, visiting the site can give you firsthand information about available units and the opportunity to ask any questions directly to the management or sales team.\n\nRemember, real estate availability can change rapidly, so it's best to check through multiple sources and act quickly if you find a unit that meets your needs.",
